{"tid":1562213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：有信心透過政府及港人努力重展對話修補分歧","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:52:56.000Z","uid":122441,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"594ff82da0e921524a274d416ec5f48bc6e1e5df","tid":1562213,"uid":122441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1jiKZxS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1jiKZxS.jpg&h=29bde639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥出席一帶一路高峰論壇致辭時提到，有信心透過政府及港人的努力，能重新展開對話，修補社會分歧。外交部駐港特派員公署特派員謝鋒批評，有極端勢力不斷將暴力升級，公然挑戰國家主權和一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n反對修訂逃犯條例示威持續三個月，行政長官林鄭月娥表示，香港受中美貿易戰影響及社會動盪正面對挑戰，她相信堅持一國兩制原則和基本法，以及政府和市民的努力，社會能修補分歧，展開對話。<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港特派員公署特派員謝鋒批評，香港一些極端勢力不斷將暴力升級，加上外國勢力干預，公然挑戰國家主權和一國兩制原則底線，呼籲各界叫停暴力及維護法治。<br />\n<br />\n謝鋒又表示，香港應該放下爭拗，抓緊一帶一路、粵港澳大灣區的發展機遇，才能拓展離岸貿易服務的空間，鞏固香港國際金融中心的地位。"},{"pid":"e4769cb418ec490c42d4b2bbdd71faefa400798e","tid":1562213,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:30:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e74a99f4bdd7fc113a64d7357afeef8dd7885b60","tid":1562213,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:44:19.000Z","msg":"6月前又講咩都唔好傾？唔洗傾？"},{"pid":"fce9009570a8a49a2e9e7a9338719f0b04b75b8a","tid":1562213,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:52:56.000Z","msg":"晒氣，佢最叻係假資詢"}]}